venue and 57th Street). A deposit\nagreement is in course of preparation and will\nshortly be filed with the depositary.\nOn and after this day, stock will be received at\neither office of the depositary, which will issue\ntemporary receipts exchangeable for defmitive cer?\ntificates of deposit, pursuant to the deposit agree?\nment.\nStock certificates must be properly endorsed ta\nblank.\nJAMES O. BLAINE, Jr., Chairman,\nVice-President, New York Trust ComptiiT.\nCHARLES E. DUNLAP,\nBerwind-White Coal Cdfnpany.\nALBERT Z. GRAY,\nGray Wilmerding.\nREG HALLJDAY,\nMackay Co.\nWALTER R. HERRiCK,\nHerrick Berg.\nTHE NEW YORK TRUST COMPANY.\n26 Broad Street,\n6th Ave. and 57th St., New York City, Devositarf.\nC. E. HUNTER, 26 Broad St., New York City, iecretar*.\nROSENBERG, BALL MARVIN, Counsel.\n3%J? ?pen- H1*h- T'ow- Laat.\n300 Armour Leath 12% 12% 12% 12%\nWO Armour pfd... 92% 92% 82% 92%\n2o Chi Pneu Tool 68 68 68 68\n100 Cont Motora.. 6% 6% 6% 6%\n40 Hartman.7:7% 777 Vi 73 >4 72U\n860 Llbby.12 12% 12* l|3\nlo0 Llndaay Light 6 6 6\n7oOMont*r7 Warfl. 18 18% 17% 18%\n9?Natl Leather.. 8% 8& 8% 8%\n40 Orpheum.27 J7 27 27\n25 Pub Svo pfd.. 82% 8S% .82* 82%7\nHOQuaker Oata.,126 125 I18 Ui\n100 Reo Motors... 22 22 22 \"2\ni^aaI**1\"8 llo?buck 87% 88% 87% 88%\n10000 Seara Roe ecp. 94 05 94 ?5\n\"15 Shaw 43 42%. 43 is?i\n2600 Stew Warner. 84% 34% 32% 33U\n100 Swift Intl. 27% 27% 27U l?2\n26 Swlft A CO...104 104*104 104\noOThompaon 33% 33% 33% 773%\n..\"Temtor Pda A. 20% 20% 20 20%\n155?*\"n Carblda... 67 67 62% 63%\ntoWeat Kntttlng 10% 10% 10% 10%\nBonda\n$1000 Ch Rys a A 6a 39 39 3S ?9\n300*) Morris lat *'-n TT 77 77\n2009 Swlft lat 5s.. 86Vi 80% 85% 8D%\nDetroit\n4200 Continental 6% 6% 8% i\\il\n55 Ford of Can.. 250 255 250 255*\n800 Lincoln Mot.. 19% lf>% l9Va '9%\n1600 Mich Sugar... 8% 8% 8% 8%\n600 Packard 10% 11 10% 11\n,i22?alro U* 18%* ls^ 1?%\n1600 Reo 22?^ 22% 21\n\nPittsburgh\nAm Roll Mille. 40 40 4*< 40\nIJ Ara Win Ol pf.101 161 101 101\n6 do Machine..106% 106% 106